# Cursor rules for Experiment Hub

> Substantive rules live in `rules/` (loaded via `.cursor/rules/` symlink).
> Skills live in `skills/` (reference `@skills/<name>.md`).
> **Edit `rules/` and `skills/` only.** This file is an index.

After clone: `bash scripts/link-agent-dirs.sh`

## Rules

**Always-applied:** `rules/principles.mdc`, `rules/github-workflow.mdc`, `rules/figma.mdc`

**File-triggered:** `rules/commit-messages.mdc`, `rules/design-guidelines.mdc`, `rules/component-conventions.mdc`, `rules/nextjs-api-routes.mdc`, `rules/vitest-conventions.mdc`, `rules/prd-template.mdc`, `rules/market-research-template.mdc`, `rules/openspec-workflow.mdc`, `rules/bhd-experiment.mdc`

## Skills

`@skills/<name>.md` — openspec-_, figma/_ (see `rules/figma.mdc`)

**OpenSpec:** `/opsx:*` stubs in `.cursor/commands/` → workflow in `skills/openspec-*.md` only (`rules/openspec-workflow.mdc`)

## Cursor-specific

- **Figma plugin:** `/add-plugin figma` in agent chat
- **MCP config:** `.cursor/mcp-config.json.example`
